name: Reporte de Ingresos
query:
select je.name, je.regnumber, je.numero_de_recibo, je.posting_date,
c.customer_name,c.company_name,c.customer_group, c.territory as 'departamento',je.en_concepto_recibo,je.tipo_de_pago, jea.mode_of_payment, jea.account_currency as 'Moneda', jea.debit_in_account_currency as 'monto_pagado',jea.exchange_rate as Tasa_de_Cambio,je.owner,je.collector as 'Colector',je.dealer as 'Dealer'
from `tabJournal Entry` je inner join `tabJournal Entry Account` jea on je.name=jea.parent inner join
`tabCustomer` c on je.regnumber=c.name
where je.docstatus=1
and jea.tipo_de_cuenta='Recibido' and je.aplicco_reversion = 0
and je.posting_date >= %(FechaD)s and je.posting_date <= %(FechaH)s
